## Integration with CHANGELOG.md

When incrementing versions, update `CHANGELOG.md` for **significant changes**:

**Update CHANGELOG.md for:**
- Major version changes (always)
- Minor version changes (usually)
- New rules, commands, standards, or checklists
- Breaking changes
- Architectural updates

**Can skip CHANGELOG.md for:**
- Patch version changes (unless significant bug fix)
- Typo fixes
- Minor clarifications

