## Version Metadata Requirements

### For All File Types

**Required Fields:**
- `version:` field in frontmatter (rules) or metadata (commands/standards/checklists)
- `lastUpdated:` field with timestamp in EST timezone
- **Format:** See `.cursor/rules/core/date-time.mdc` Section 3 (authoritative source)

**Getting Current Timestamp:**
- **See `.cursor/rules/core/date-time.mdc` Section 3 for authoritative date format and command**
- Get timestamp ONLY when ready to write (not as first step)

